<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>kl ywm tḥt ṣlybk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 kl ywm tḥt ṣlybk knt bạfkr dạymạaⁿ fyk yạrby wạ̉jylk

[V2]
 mn gẖyr kẖwf zy ạ̉bwyạ ʿn ạ̉srạry wʿn ḥkạytny hnạk bạḥkylk

[V3]
 knt ktyr yạ rby bạfkr mn dlwqty wḥty̱ ạ̉mạ ạ̉kbr

[V4]
 ạ̹ny lạ ymkn ywm hạtgẖyr wạ̉nsy̱ ṣlybk

[V5]
 knt fy qlby dạymạaⁿ ạ̉ṣly yfḍl ḥbk fy tmly wmạfysẖ ḥạjẗ fy ywm tmnʿny ạ̹n ạ̉jylk wạfḍl ạ̉ḥkylk

[V6]
 wạ̉mạ kbr nạdytk tạny bs lqyt fy ạ̹ydy yạrby qywd mnʿạny

[V7]
