[V13]
 msḥt dmwʿy jddt kyạny bạʿtrạfạt mn ʿmq ạlqlb ndm jwạny

[V14]
 wạ̹zạy bqy̱ yạ rb hạkạfỷk wʿly̱ rʿạytk

[V15]
 hạfḍl ṭwl ạlwqt ạ̉ṭạwʿk jwh ṭryqk

[V16]
 wykwn qlby byrnm lk ṭwl ạlʿmr hạmjd ạsmk

[V17]
 ạ̉gẖly mạ ʿndh byqdmlk lmạ ạ̉jylk</lyrics>
